{
  "name": "graj",
  "permissions": "NONE",
  "restriction": "1",
  "_id": "dfaXI",
  "actions": [
    {
      "info": "1",

      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "search",
      "name": "Store Command Params"
    },
    {
      "server": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "storage": "1",
      "varName2": "botmem",
      "name": "Get Bot as Member"
    },
    {
      "video": "${tempVars(\"search\")}",
      "key": "TUTAJ_KLUCZ",
      "info": "6",
      "resultNo": "0",
      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "videokind",
      "name": "YouTube Search"
    },
    {
      "token": "",
      "user": "",
      "pass": "",
      "url": "https://www.googleapis.com/youtube/v3/search?part=snippet&maxResults=5&q=${tempVars(\"search\")}&key=TUTAJ_KLUCZ",
      "path": "items[0].snippet.channelTitle",
      "storage": "2",
      "varName": "channel",
      "debugMode": "1",
      "headers": "",
      "name": "Store Json From WebAPI"
    },
    {
      "token": "",
      "user": "",
      "pass": "",

    {

      "path": "items[0].snippet.thumbnails.default.url",
      "storage": "2",
      "varName": "coverart",
      "debugMode": "1",
      "headers": "",
      "name": "Store Json From WebAPI"
    },
    {
      "token": "",
      "user": "",
      "pass": "",
      "url": "https://www.googleapis.com/youtube/v3/search?part=snippet&maxResults=5&q=${tempVars(\"search\")}&key=TUTAJ_KLUCZ",
      "path": "items[0].snippet.title",
      "storage": "2",
      "varName": "title",

    {

      "url": "https://www.googleapis.com/youtube/v3/search?part=snippet&maxResults=5&q=${tempVars(\"search\")}&key=TUTAJ_KLUCZ",
      "path": "items[0].id.videoId",
      "storage": "2",
      "varName": "url",
      "debugMode": "1",
      "headers": "",
      "name": "Store Json From WebAPI"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "info": "2",
      "storage": "1",
      "varName2": "playchannel",
      "name": "Store Voice Channel Info"
    },
    {
      "title": "▶️ Teraz Gramy: ${serverVars(\"title\")}",
      "author": "",
      "color": "#0080FF",
      "timestamp": "true",

      "authorIcon": "",

      "name": "Add Embed Field"
    },
    {
      "storage": "1",

      "name": "End Action Sequence"
